# Nested slots demonstration
# Shows how slots create layer hierarchy

# Root node (layer 0) with nested slots
@page |style.title=<<My Document>>|@header |style.title=<<Header>>|<<<Top of the page>>>|.|@body |@intro |<<<Welcome to this example>>>|.|@content |<<<Main content goes here>>>|.|.|@footer |<<<Copyright 2026>>>|.|.

# Layers:
#   @page = 0
#   @header = 1, @body = 1, @footer = 1
#   @intro = 2, @content = 2

@out |$page|.
